* Initial version:
Work started from cadence-sample.
Why we chose Cadence,

1. Super Fast & Concurrency guaranteed & HA
Comparing to Airflow, it is super fast to run short living, concurrent jobs.
Comparing to Celery, it is powerful enough to run complicate DAGs or long time schedules (1 day, 1 month, 1 yr etc.)
Comparing to Netflix Conductor, it is more extensible and flexible with code defined workflow, more lightweight yet powerful.

2. Workflow features can be easily added in a few line - Workflow as Code
Initial DAG implements features includes,
Dynamic runtime DAG support
Easily Query build based on a workflow.
Platform - Worker - Client decoupling.
Fully distributed workers, able to do rolling upgrade.
Versionized task management and executable.
Scalable based on Cassandra or SQL.
Open source project support.